OL,3,CCampaigners are 'cautiously pleased'
OL,4,Cafter Welsh Water revises Pontsarn
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FCampaigners in Merthyr Tydfil say
OL,8,Fthey're "cautiously pleased" that
OL,9,FWelsh Water has abandoned plans for a
OL,10,Fnew treatment works on a special
OL,11,Flandscape area.
OL,13,FCommunity group "Protect Pontsarn" has
OL,14,Ffought development of the site for
OL,15,Fmore than two years.
OL,17,FWelsh Water say they will now upgrade
OL,18,Fexisting works, and build a smaller
OL,19,Fnew site instead.
