OL,3,CCampaigners are 'cautiously pleased'
OL,4,Cafter Welsh Water revises Pontsarn
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FBut campaigners say they'll be
OL,8,Fscrutinising the revised plans for any
OL,9,Fenvironmental impact.
OL,11,FCampaigner Mog Chambers said : "This
OL,12,Fis part of an ancient landscape.
OL,13,FPeople have worked this area three and
OL,14,Fa half thousand years ago."
OL,16,FPeople trying to protect Pontsarn say
OL,17,Fthat new plans from Welsh Water would
OL,18,Fstill involve building on fields used
OL,19,Ffor grazing.
