OL,7,FSo they'll be paying close attention
OL,8,Fto detail.
OL,10,FBut they say they've fought Welsh
OL,11,FWater and got victory in the first
OL,12,Fbattle.
OL,14,FAnother campaigner, Lee Johnson said
OL,15,F:"For a community to take on a huge
OL,16,Fdeveloper and win locally is
OL,17,Funprecedented. So yes, it is a
OL,18,Fmilestone. We've got to thank all of
OL,19,Four five thousand members for the time
OL,20,Fand contribution they've made. And we
OL,21,Finvite more people to come along now."
