OL,3,CCampaigners are 'cautiously pleased'
OL,4,Cafter Welsh Water revises Pontsarn
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FSome of the existing water treatment
OL,8,Fplants will now be upgraded as part of
OL,9,FWelsh Water's proposals to provide
OL,10,Fclean drinking water in the future.
OL,12,FAnd they'll develop further on land
OL,13,Fthey already own. That construction
OL,14,Fhas long been called for locally.
OL,16,FIt'll see huge investment, and the
OL,17,Fdemolition of old derelict buildings.
OL,19,FWelsh Water say they've listened to
OL,20,Fcustomers.
