OL,3,CCampaigners are 'cautiously pleased'
OL,4,Cafter Welsh Water revises Pontsarn
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FLocal people say it's a move in the
OL,8,Fright direction. But they wonder if it
OL,9,Fcould be placed away from Pontsarn
OL,10,Fentirely.
OL,12,FCampaigner Mog Chambers said: "They'd
OL,13,Ftold us that they'd tried twelve
OL,14,Fplaces, and this was the only one they
OL,15,Fcould use. And lo and behold, they've
OL,16,Fmoved four hundred yards up the road
OL,17,Finto a site. And that's ok. But it's
OL,18,Fstill in Pontsarn. It's still in the
OL,19,Fsame area where people have trod for
OL,20,Fmany many years."
